<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَيُؤْمِنُ لِلْمُؤْمِنِينَ}</span> ... يُصَدِّقُ المُؤْمِنِينَ فِيمَا يُخْبِرُونَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
